    "Pinned OCI SDK contract: CreateVbsInstance, GetVbsInstance, ListVbsInstances, ChangeVbsInstanceCompartment, UpdateVbsInstance, DeleteVbsInstance, and GetWorkRequest are present in v65.110.0. ListVbsInstances filters compartmentId, id, name, and lifecycleState, while the CRUD mutation responses expose opc-work-request-id but do not return a VbsInstance body.",
